NK034(ngi)002:1: bstan pa bu gcig gi rgyud gser gyi snying po
NK034(ngi)002:2: nyi ma rab tu snang byed bzhugs so rgya gar
NK034(ngi)002:3: skad du bud+d+ha sarba bu tra e ka gu h+ya
NK034(ngi)002:4: pu ri sa man tan+t+ra n+aa mah bod skad du
NK034(ngi)002:5: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sras gcig po gsang ba
NK034(ngi)002:6: thams cad gcod pa sa bon gyi rgyud ces bya
NK034(ngi)002:7: ba dran pa kun gyi thog ma yi dngos mdzad
NK034(ngi)002:8: sangs rgyas thog ma la dang po nyid du phyag
NK034(ngi)002:9: 'tshal lo 'di skad bdag la sogs pa yi sangs
NK034(ngi)002:10: rgyas bye ba dung phyur gyi dgongs pa nyid dang
NK034(ngi)002:11: grangs med par thugs kyi snying po ji lta bar
NK034(ngi)002:12: gsungs shing bstan pa'i dus gcig na mya ngan 'das
NK034(ngi)002:13: pa'i thog mar ni 'di ni nyag cig rnal ma
NK034(ngi)002:14: yin don gyi sa bon rnams su ni nges pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:15: snying po nyid du yang gsungs so bstan to bshad
NK034(ngi)002:16: pa yin bstan pa'i don ni rgya mtsho kun la
NK034(ngi)002:17: la gnas skabs yul don du la la ma 'ongs
NK034(ngi)002:18: 'jug don yin la la 'dul don tha dad nyid
NK034(ngi)002:19: snying gi snying po tshig 'ga' las kun gyis grub
NK034(ngi)002:20: pa ma yin no bstan pa 'phel byed sa bon
NK034(ngi)002:21: du 'di kun bzhag cing byin brlabs las rang byung
NK034(ngi)002:22: nyid du thugs las rdol de phyir sangs rgyas thams
NK034(ngi)002:23: cad kyi thugs kyi sras ni gcig par yang rang
NK034(ngi)002:24: byung chen po'i 'phel dang bcas 'byung ba'i dgra dang
NK034(ngi)002:25: bral bar byung 'di ni bstan pa gang byung du
NK034(ngi)002:26: 'od dang bcas te 'byung ba yin gang la babs
NK034(ngi)002:27: par gyur pa'i mi bstan pa kun gyi bdag por
NK034(ngi)002:28: 'gyur 'di la ldem por bstan pa med sus kyang
NK034(ngi)002:29: bshad cing nyan med par rang byung dgongs pa klong
NK034(ngi)002:30: rdol du nyi ma sprin las thon pa bzhin sus
NK034(ngi)002:31: kyang ma bsgribs rang byung ngo 'di la 'byung bzhi'i
NK034(ngi)002:32: gnod med pas nam mkha' dag la 'phar bar snang
NK034(ngi)002:33: sangs rgyas 'bras bu sus thob pa 'di nyid de
NK034(ngi)002:34: las snang ba yin 'di ma mthong ba'i sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)002:35: ni gcig kyang 'byung ba snga phyir med de phyir
NK034(ngi)002:36: bstan pa rnams kyi btsas sangs rgyas kun gyi sras
NK034(ngi)002:37: gcig po myang 'das thob pa'i sna thag yin dgongs
NK034(ngi)002:38: pa rang thog 'bebs pa yi gnad kyi tshig tu
NK034(ngi)002:39: 'di nyid byung 'jig rten khams ni gang du yang
NK034(ngi)002:40: sangs rgyas nyid ni sus thob pa de tshe 'di
NK034(ngi)002:41: ni lan gsum du nam mkha' dag la 'phar ba
NK034(ngi)002:42: dang rang 'od lnga po 'di las byung 'di 'dzin
NK034(ngi)002:43: rnal 'byor skal che bas lan gsum 'di yi tshig
NK034(ngi)002:44: kun yang lhag dang chad pa med par ni rdo
NK034(ngi)002:45: rje'i lce yis sus brjod na 'di yang de dang
NK034(ngi)002:46: mnyam par yang 'gyur ba 'di la the tshom med
NK034(ngi)002:47: de phyir bstan pa'i rgyud rnams kun thams cad dus
NK034(ngi)002:48: gcig sgom shes kyang 'di ma snang bar grol ba
NK034(ngi)002:49: med 'di ni sa bon rang 'phel bas bstan pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:50: bdag po gang sangs rgyas 'di nyid sa bon med
NK034(ngi)002:51: par ni bstan pa'i gsung ni tshig tsam yang lce
NK034(ngi)002:52: yi dbang pos brjod mi nus de tshig 'di la
NK034(ngi)002:53: ma brten par rdul cha tsam yang 'byung ba min
NK034(ngi)002:54: bstan pa gcig gi snyigs ma la byin brlabs tshig
NK034(ngi)002:55: ni 'di kun yang gang la snang ba'i mi des
NK034(ngi)002:56: kyang ma mthong rgyud dang bstan bcos ni lce yi
NK034(ngi)002:57: dbang pos brjod par nus sems can kun gyi bsam
NK034(ngi)002:58: pa dang sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa dang ji
NK034(ngi)002:59: ltar mthun pa'i chos kun ni 'di yis ston par
NK034(ngi)002:60: nus pa yin sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs dang gcig
NK034(ngi)002:61: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i dgongs pa dang dbyer mi phyed
NK034(ngi)002:62: par 'dis 'gyur ro de phyir bstan pa'i me ro
NK034(ngi)002:63: yin rang byung tshig gi rgyal po 'di so so'i
NK034(ngi)002:64: sems can skye gzugs la so so'i brda skad ci
NK034(ngi)002:65: lta bar 'di nyid de ltar snang ba yin de
NK034(ngi)002:66: phyir rang byung yi ger ni thog ma babs kyis
NK034(ngi)002:67: grub nas byung rang byung bcom ldan 'das la yang
NK034(ngi)002:68: 'di ltar rdzogs pa'i lugs su snang chos kyi sde
NK034(ngi)002:69: snod nyid du ni 'di tshig ye nas rang shar
NK034(ngi)002:70: bas thog ma dran pa'i gzhir gyur te dran pa
NK034(ngi)002:71: thams cad ma stongs par tshig 'di kun kyang snang
NK034(ngi)002:72: ba yi dran zad tshig 'di zad par ni rdo
NK034(ngi)002:73: rje zhes ni tshig 'di kun 'byung ba'i rkyen dang
NK034(ngi)002:74: bral bas na rdo rje kun 'byung gsang sngags yin
NK034(ngi)002:75: thabs lam du ma mtshon pa'i phyir rang babs bsgom
NK034(ngi)002:76: pa 'di las byung snying po rang 'dul bstan pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:77: bcud gzhi nyid kyi ni babs yin no chos kun
NK034(ngi)002:78: mnyam pa'i nan tan tshig rang gnad du ni 'di
NK034(ngi)002:79: kun shar 'di la nub pa gcig nyid med bsgom
NK034(ngi)002:80: dang bsgrub pa'i rtsa bar yang 'di sngags 'khrul ba'i
NK034(ngi)002:81: tshig ma yin ma 'khrul sngon thog nyid kyi gzhi
NK034(ngi)002:82: 'di las 'phros pas spros pa'i rgyud rgyu las 'bras
NK034(ngi)002:83: bu rang byung bzhin 'di nyid las ni tshig kun
NK034(ngi)002:84: yang dran bsam bral ba'i ngang nyid las byas pa
NK034(ngi)002:85: med par byung ba yin 'od zer 'dzin pa'i skyes
NK034(ngi)002:86: bu la 'di ni snang bar 'gyur ba'o de las
NK034(ngi)002:87: 'phel nas grangs 'ga' 'byung gsang ba'i bden pa gcig
NK034(ngi)002:88: pa nyid grangs med rdo rje 'chang rnams kyi thugs
NK034(ngi)002:89: rdol nyag gcig dgongs don gcig 'dzin med yangs pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:90: gtod phur yin thod rgal thog babs kun gyi gnad
NK034(ngi)002:91: rang sa 'byed pa'i lde mig mchog 'di ni bde
NK034(ngi)002:92: ba'i sa bon 'dzin sangs rgyas rnams kyi shes rab
NK034(ngi)002:93: yin mkha' mnyam dag pa'i rnam gzir 'dis bstan pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:94: kun gyi rtsa ba 'dzin 'di yis grangs sna bzung
NK034(ngi)002:95: bas na lha min g.yul rnams rang log tu 'di
NK034(ngi)002:96: tshig bzung ba tsam gyis 'gyur khams gsum g.yul kun
NK034(ngi)002:97: 'dis bzlog go rigs drug rnams kyi 'bros khungs 'gegs
NK034(ngi)002:98: mya ngan med pa'i grong khyer du 'jug par byed
NK034(ngi)002:99: pa'i 'khor lo yin sred pas bcings pa rnams la
NK034(ngi)002:100: ni 'di yis grol bar byed pa'o dam pa'i snying
NK034(ngi)002:101: po gdung rgyud du rang bzhin du ni babs las
NK034(ngi)002:102: byung 'dis ni bla ma'i sku mi spong snying la
NK034(ngi)002:103: nyi ma'i 'od brdal bas phyogs bcur khyab pa'i mun
NK034(ngi)002:104: pa ni 'di yis rang sangs nyid du 'gro lhag
NK034(ngi)002:105: par gnas pa'i ye shes ni 'di yis mchog tu
NK034(ngi)002:106: ston par byed dkon pa'i mchog rnams bskyed pa'i yum
NK034(ngi)002:107: sems dal bsam gtan ngang gis 'grub chos sku'i snang
NK034(ngi)002:108: ba dus gcig tu ston par byed pa'i sgron ma'o
NK034(ngi)002:109: phyin ci log las yang dag tu dag par byed
NK034(ngi)002:110: pa'i chu rgyun yin theg pa kun gyi mthar thug
NK034(ngi)002:111: tu skyel bar byed pa'i shing rta'o thos bsam sgom
NK034(ngi)002:112: pa'i rgyangs shing du 'jug par byed pa'i dngos po
NK034(ngi)002:113: yin sde snod thams cad 'dzin pa yi mnyen lcugs
NK034(ngi)002:114: ldan pa'i lcags kyu'o rnal 'byor dag pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK034(ngi)002:115: gyi lam du 'jug pa'i sa mkhan yin mngal rnams
NK034(ngi)002:116: khungs sgo 'gegs par byed thar pa'i skas ni rang
NK034(ngi)002:117: 'dzugs yin rnam dag 'od kyi mthongs 'byed pa chos
NK034(ngi)002:118: rnams kyi ni re gnas sa bdud dang mu stegs
NK034(ngi)002:119: mgo gnon yin shes pa rmugs pa'i gsal 'debs so
NK034(ngi)002:120: smon 'jug kun gyi srog shing yin lha dang sngags
NK034(ngi)002:121: kyi mdo mdud do dkyil 'khor rnams kyi skyed shing
NK034(ngi)002:122: ngo lta sgom log pa'i dag byed khrus man ngag
NK034(ngi)002:123: snying po rdzogs pa'i sa rdo rje theg pa'i grangs
NK034(ngi)002:124: rdzogs nas 'gro rnams lam la 'dzud pa'o theg pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:125: rgyal po yongs rdzogs kyi yon tan byung tshul rang
NK034(ngi)002:126: byung ngo e ma ho gsang mdzad rang bzhin tshig
NK034(ngi)002:127: 'di yang rang byung ye dag chen por ni spel
NK034(ngi)002:128: tshig gsang ba 'di ltar snang ye thog dang po'i
NK034(ngi)002:129: sangs rgyas ni dang po mngon 'phags dran pa mgon
NK034(ngi)002:130: phyag rgya rang dran 'khor lo ni gzhi las 'phags
NK034(ngi)002:131: pa'i khyad par tshig spyi phud sngon gyi thog mar
NK034(ngi)002:132: byung 'di dus khrag khrig bdun cu yis phyag rgya
NK034(ngi)002:133: 'di ni dam pa'o snying pos brgyan pa'i bskal pa
NK034(ngi)002:134: la sde snod dang po'i sangs rgyas mgon mnga' mdzad
NK034(ngi)002:135: phyag rgya 'khor lo las 'khor ni 'dzin pa bye
NK034(ngi)002:136: ba lnga phyag rgya 'di ni dam pa'o spyi mes
NK034(ngi)002:137: dang po pha rol mgon dkyil 'khor snying po rang
NK034(ngi)002:138: spros pas bskal pa gser gyi yi ge la sa
NK034(ngi)002:139: ya drug gi phyag rgyar bzung sngon thog dang po
NK034(ngi)002:140: 'phags pa mgon phyag rgya dngos po nyid snang bas
NK034(ngi)002:141: bskal pa 'od zer 'byed pa la bdud 'bum gyi
NK034(ngi)002:142: ni 'bras bu'o 'jig rten d+r+wa ba mgon po yis
NK034(ngi)002:143: spros bral phyag rgya 'di spros te bskal pa me
NK034(ngi)002:144: tog mdzes pa la bstan pa'i 'bras bu phyal yal
NK034(ngi)002:145: las phyag rgya 'di ni dam pa'o snying po stong
NK034(ngi)002:146: gi spyi phud mgon snying po dam pa'i 'khor lo
NK034(ngi)002:147: las bskal pa rtsod pa'i snying po la grangs med
NK034(ngi)002:148: bzhi yi snying po'o 'od ldan dang po sems can
NK034(ngi)002:149: mgon spros med snying po rang sgra las bskal ba
NK034(ngi)002:150: snang ba'i sgron ma la ban bun stong gi phyag
NK034(ngi)002:151: rgyar bzung mdzes pa'i dang po 'gro ba'i mgon yang
NK034(ngi)002:152: dag snying po rnams spros te bskal pa rags pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:153: yan lag la nyar nyer brgya yi grangs kyis ni
NK034(ngi)002:154: phyag rgya 'di ni dam pa'o thugs brtse snying po
NK034(ngi)002:155: nyan thos mgon phyag rgya yang dag lam spros te
NK034(ngi)002:156: bskal pa dung gi sgra dag la greng greng bcu
NK034(ngi)002:157: yi dam par ro mi pham zang ma sgra bral
NK034(ngi)002:158: mgon yang dag nges pa'i rgyud las ni bskal pa
NK034(ngi)002:159: d+r+wa ba'i 'od zer la dung phyur bdun t+ai kar
NK034(ngi)002:160: gsum snang / gyis lam rgyal bzung snying po sems
NK034(ngi)002:161: rnal bdud rtsi mgon nges pa'i sa bon rab bsgrags
NK034(ngi)002:162: pas bskal pa tshangs pa'i dbyangs can la 'bur rdul
NK034(ngi)002:163: bdun gyis nges par bzung rang bzhin drag po ting
NK034(ngi)002:164: 'dzin mgon phyag rgya 'khor lo bden spros te bskal
NK034(ngi)002:165: pa smra ba'i gzhi dag la phyal phyol dgu yis
NK034(ngi)002:166: dam par bzung gsang ba phyag rgya lha min mgon
NK034(ngi)002:167: yang gsang 'khor lo rnam spros te bskal pa 'bum
NK034(ngi)002:168: pa reg ldan la yal yol drug cus snying po'o
NK034(ngi)002:169: rim pa lnga pa gtsug phud mgon bla med snying
NK034(ngi)002:170: po yongs spros pas bskal pa yang gsal rab 'byams
NK034(ngi)002:171: la khrag khrig bye ba dgu brgya yis bla na
NK034(ngi)002:172: med pa'i gsang ba'o 'jig rten thog ma shes rab
NK034(ngi)002:173: mgon bde chen snying po yongs spros te bskal pa
NK034(ngi)002:174: bkod pa chen po la 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa
NK034(ngi)002:175: bzhi yis lha yi lhar ni 'di nyid do 'chang
NK034(ngi)002:176: ba rnams kyis thog ma mgon nges pa'i 'bras bu
NK034(ngi)002:177: 'di spros te bskal pa rin chen spungs pa la
NK034(ngi)002:178: sa ya dgu bcu'i mgon po yis rgyas par basngagasa
NK034(ngi)002:179: te dam par ro yang rjes 'byung ba me 'od
NK034(ngi)002:180: mgon dngos po bsgyur ba'i phyag rgya ni snying po
NK034(ngi)002:181: nyid du spros pa las bskal pa rab tu g.yo
NK034(ngi)002:182: med la rab mtha' bcu yi mgon po yis snying
NK034(ngi)002:183: po snying gi dwangs mar ro chags med rdul bral
NK034(ngi)002:184: dri med mgon gsang chen nges pa nyid du ste
NK034(ngi)002:185: bskal pa g.yo sgyu bral ba la bye ba dgu
NK034(ngi)002:186: khri'i grangs mgon gyis 'du ba'i phyag rgya nyid du'o
NK034(ngi)002:187: dran pa dri med bsam gtan mgon dri med nges
NK034(ngi)002:188: pa'i gsang tshig spros bskal pa mtha' ldan seng ge
NK034(ngi)002:189: la nyal nyil sum cu'i rgyal ba yis 'di ni
NK034(ngi)002:190: bden tshig dam par ro dam pa'i skyes bu chos
NK034(ngi)002:191: kyi mgon sangs rgyas shes rab sa bon spros bskal
NK034(ngi)002:192: pa gdung ba sel ba la sang seng dgu khri'i
NK034(ngi)002:193: gdung 'phel bas dam pa'i phyag ni yang dam du'o
NK034(ngi)002:194: spyi phud stong gi ye thog mgon sngags kyi rtsa
NK034(ngi)002:195: ba 'di basngagasa pas bskal pa dung gi snying po
NK034(ngi)002:196: la kha yel stong gi gdung 'phel bas gsang chen
NK034(ngi)002:197: dam par rab bzung ba'o sangs rgyas d+r+wa ba mgon
NK034(ngi)002:198: po yis phyag rgya nyid du gdung gzung bas bskal
NK034(ngi)002:199: pa bye ba'i snying po la nyag thag khri yi
NK034(ngi)002:200: gdung 'dzin pas 'di nyid snying po'i don du'o yang
NK034(ngi)002:201: dag gsang ba pad+ma mgon snying gi snying po dkyil
NK034(ngi)002:202: bzung bas bskal pa yongs su brtse ba la deng
NK034(ngi)002:203: dir stong gi yang 'phel bas 'di ni snying la
NK034(ngi)002:204: yang dag spros sems can snying brtse me tog mgon
NK034(ngi)002:205: dran gzhi dang po rab bzung bas bskal pa yod
NK034(ngi)002:206: pa rab mchog la rdul med dgu yi gsang 'dzin
NK034(ngi)002:207: pas gsang chen stong gi dam par ro bskal pa
NK034(ngi)002:208: d+r+wa ba nyi 'od mgon dam pa'i snying po nges
NK034(ngi)002:209: phab pas bskal pa glang po yongs rdzogs la rab
NK034(ngi)002:210: rdul nyid kyi rjes 'dzin pas stong nyid gsal ba'i
NK034(ngi)002:211: mig tu spros yongs rdzogs 'khor lo rigs kyi mgon
NK034(ngi)002:212: sems kyi dngos po dam par bzung bskal pa bla
NK034(ngi)002:213: na med pa la khri phrag drug cu'i gdung 'phel
NK034(ngi)002:214: bas gsang chen 'khor lo nyid du 'o dri med
NK034(ngi)002:215: dag pa chos kyi mgon yang gsang nges pa'i lung
NK034(ngi)002:216: 'di spros bskal pa rtsod pa rang grol la nyal
NK034(ngi)002:217: nyil nyid kyi 'phel gdung gis rim pas mngon par
NK034(ngi)002:218: rab spros pa'o yang gsang dang po thog ma mgon
NK034(ngi)002:219: rdo rje yang dag dam bzung bas bskal pa khyung
NK034(ngi)002:220: chen gshog rdzogs la 'bum phrag lnga yi gdung 'phel
NK034(ngi)002:221: bas phyag rgya rang rdzogs nyid du'o snang mdzad dang
NK034(ngi)002:222: po mar me mgon bla med rdo rje snying po
NK034(ngi)002:223: spros bskal pa mda' yis yongs bzung la rnga yab
NK034(ngi)002:224: gsum gyi gdung 'phel bas rigs ldan rnams kyi phyag
NK034(ngi)002:225: tu bzung yid shes dang po gnas gsum mgon snying
NK034(ngi)002:226: thig rtsa ba'i dwangs mar spros bskal pa rig pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:227: stobs can la kha yel drug gi gdung 'phel bas
NK034(ngi)002:228: gong 'phel phyag rgya dam par spros dpa' bo 'jigs
NK034(ngi)002:229: sangs dang po'i mgon dri ma med pa'i snying du
NK034(ngi)002:230: babs bskal pa dran bsam bral ba la yal yol
NK034(ngi)002:231: stong gi gdung 'phel bas 'di kun skyon dang bral
NK034(ngi)002:232: bar ro drag po chags bral bde ba'i mgon chags
NK034(ngi)002:233: med rang rig phyag rgya spros bskal pa mya ngan
NK034(ngi)002:234: bral ba la dung phyur gsum gyi gdung 'phel bas
NK034(ngi)002:235: med pa rnams kyi dang por ro chos sku dngos
NK034(ngi)002:236: dag dri med mgon dam pa gsung gi snying po
NK034(ngi)002:237: spros bskal pa zil gyis gnon pa la sa ya
NK034(ngi)002:238: nyid kyi gdung 'phel bas 'di kun yang dag nyid
NK034(ngi)002:239: du'o yang gsang rgyas pa sgyu ma mgon tshig bral
NK034(ngi)002:240: bden pa'i snying po spros bskal pa chos kyi 'khor
NK034(ngi)002:241: lo la bya ba dgu yi gdung 'phel bas nges
NK034(ngi)002:242: pa'i lam gyi dwangs mar ro stong pa nyid ni
NK034(ngi)002:243: dge ldan mgon gsang ba'i yang gsang chen por spros
NK034(ngi)002:244: bskal pa pad+ma brtsegs pa la kha yel lnga yi
NK034(ngi)002:245: gdung 'phel bas snang ba rnams kyi thog mar ro
NK034(ngi)002:246: skyes bu byed pa 'od zer mgon 'bras bu rdzogs
NK034(ngi)002:247: pa'i rim pa spros bskal pa ngang pa'i dbyangs can
NK034(ngi)002:248: la rdul mtha' bzhi yi gdung 'phel bas 'di kun
NK034(ngi)002:249: mngon par rang 'thad do shes rab mig rnyed sgyu
NK034(ngi)002:250: 'phrul mgon sems nyid thog ma'i dkyil 'khor spros bskal
NK034(ngi)002:251: pa lha yi phyag sor la nyal nyil bdun gyi
NK034(ngi)002:252: gdung 'dzin pas snying po rang dag gnad du'o bde
NK034(ngi)002:253: ba dam pa dngos grub mgon gsang chen snying po
NK034(ngi)002:254: dam par spros bskal pa yan lag med pa la
NK034(ngi)002:255: sang seng drug gi gdung 'phel bas 'di kun yang
NK034(ngi)002:256: dag dam par ro dngos po yang dag stong pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:257: mgon skyob pa dam pa'i phyag rgya spros bskal pa
NK034(ngi)002:258: grangs mtha' log pa la stong phrag dgu yi grangs
NK034(ngi)002:259: 'dzin pas rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nyid du'o chos kyi
NK034(ngi)002:260: grags pa gnyis med mgon yang gsang rang byung tshig
NK034(ngi)002:261: 'di spros bskal pa yongs su grol byed la nyal
NK034(ngi)002:262: nyil gsum gyi gdung 'phel bas mnyam pa rang gnad
NK034(ngi)002:263: nyid du'o ye nas gsang ba dri med mgon byin
NK034(ngi)002:264: brlabs rang byung yi ge spros bskal pa seng ge
NK034(ngi)002:265: rtsal sprug la khrag khrig bdun gyi gdung 'phel bas
NK034(ngi)002:266: 'di kun dam pa'i thugs dkyil du'o mi pham dang
NK034(ngi)002:267: po sangs rgyas mgon gsang ba thugs kyi bu gcig
NK034(ngi)002:268: par bskal pa dga' bas myos pa la dung phyur
NK034(ngi)002:269: phyed dang dgu gdung gis 'di nyid dmigs med rang
NK034(ngi)002:270: dam du'o dran spangs mngon 'phags rang bzhin mgon 'byung
NK034(ngi)002:271: ba'i dgra dang bral bar spros bskal pa 'du ba
NK034(ngi)002:272: chen po la kha yel lnga yi gdung 'phel bas
NK034(ngi)002:273: 'di tshig rang byung gsal bar ro bar ma'i dang
NK034(ngi)002:274: po skye med mgon 'di ni phyag rgya rab btab
NK034(ngi)002:275: ste bskal pa khu byug rang byung la thar ther
NK034(ngi)002:276: gsum gyi rtags shar bas 'di ni rab tu basngagasa
NK034(ngi)002:277: pa'o 'jig rten grangs bskal ut+pala mgon gsang chen rab
NK034(ngi)002:278: rgyas phyag rgya spros bskal pa rab tu mthong ba
NK034(ngi)002:279: la 'bum phrag dgu yi gdung 'phel bas 'di kun
NK034(ngi)002:280: snying gi dkyil du phob 'das pa'i dang po d+r+wa
NK034(ngi)002:281: ba mgon ston pa gsang ba yang dag spros bskal
NK034(ngi)002:282: pa bud med rang 'dul la phyal phyol dgu yi
NK034(ngi)002:283: rgyal ba yis 'di tshig rang rig dam par ro
NK034(ngi)002:284: gnyis 'das dang po zhing khams mgon rdo rje chen
NK034(ngi)002:285: po'i gsang tshig spros bskal bar rang sgra zad pa
NK034(ngi)002:286: la sa ya gnyis kyi gdung 'phel bas 'di tshig
NK034(ngi)002:287: gzigs dang rab mkhyen bzung grub mtha' thog ma gnyis
NK034(ngi)002:288: par mgon 'dul tshig snying po bla ma spros bskal
NK034(ngi)002:289: pa dge ldan chen po la 'bum phrag lnga yi
NK034(ngi)002:290: gdung 'phel bas snying po rnams kyi yang snying du'o
NK034(ngi)002:291: mdzad pa gzhi thog thod rgal mgon bla na med
NK034(ngi)002:292: pa'i nges lung spros bskal pa bram ze bsgyings pa
NK034(ngi)002:293: la khri phrag dgu yi gdung 'phel bas 'di kun
NK034(ngi)002:294: gsang ba'i tshig tu'o mtha' bral yongs rdzogs skyon bral
NK034(ngi)002:295: mgon bral gsang tshig 'di phyag rgyas spros bskal pa
NK034(ngi)002:296: skyed par byed pa la stong phrag dgu yi gdung
NK034(ngi)002:297: 'phel bas med tshig rdzogs par yang dag bzung ye
NK034(ngi)002:298: rdzogs dang po sgyu ma mgon yang gsang 'bar ba
NK034(ngi)002:299: 'od zer spros bskal pa rab tu 'phags pa la
NK034(ngi)002:300: khrag khrig gnyis kyi gdung 'phel bas 'di nyid nges
NK034(ngi)002:301: pa'i gsang chen no dri ma dngos bral bde ba'i
NK034(ngi)002:302: mgon 'di nyid lam rgyal dam par spros bskal pa
NK034(ngi)002:303: yang gsang chen po la khrag khrig bdun gyi gdung
NK034(ngi)002:304: 'phel bas 'di tshig rim pa dang por spros 'dus
NK034(ngi)002:305: pa rnams kyi thog ma mgon nges pa'i gsang chen
NK034(ngi)002:306: rab basngagasa te bskal pa gser 'od dam pa la
NK034(ngi)002:307: yang 'phel dgu khri'i mgon po yis 'di kun gsang
NK034(ngi)002:308: chen snying du bab yang 'byed stong gi dang po
NK034(ngi)002:309: mgon gsang ba'i snying po yang gsang spros bskal pa
NK034(ngi)002:310: le lo ye dag la ther zug dgu yi gdung
NK034(ngi)002:311: 'phel bas 'di yang snying thig gsang bar bab gsang
NK034(ngi)002:312: ba kun gyi mngon thog mgon phyag rgya snying gi
NK034(ngi)002:313: dkyil du spros bskal pa dri med bzang po la
NK034(ngi)002:314: nyar nyer lnga yi gdung 'phel bas 'di tshig bla
NK034(ngi)002:315: med snying la bab ston pa'i dang po nam mkha'
NK034(ngi)002:316: mgon yang bsdus rang byung tshig 'di spros bskal pa
NK034(ngi)002:317: thar chags chen po la nyal nyil drug gi gdung
NK034(ngi)002:318: 'phel bas 'di nyid bsam gtan 'khor lor bzung stong
NK034(ngi)002:319: pa'i yang mdzod dam pa mgon 'di kun g.yo med
NK034(ngi)002:320: rang byung tshig rdzogs pa dngos dag bskal pa la
NK034(ngi)002:321: 'bum phrag dgu yi yang gdung gis 'di kun nges
NK034(ngi)002:322: pa'i 'bras bur spros dang po gsang 'dzin dngos grub
NK034(ngi)002:323: mgon 'di yang mdzad chen dag par spros bskal pa
NK034(ngi)002:324: grangs brdal gsang chen la kha yel gsum gyi gdung
NK034(ngi)002:325: 'phel bas 'di kun yang dag lam nyer bzung dri
NK034(ngi)002:326: med rang zad 'byung bral mgon dkyil 'khor kun dag
NK034(ngi)002:327: rtsa ba spros bskal pa mo mtshan rgyun gcod la
NK034(ngi)002:328: thar ther brgya yi gdung 'phel bas gsang ba'i yang
NK034(ngi)002:329: zhun thigs par bzung mos chen rnams kyi dang po
NK034(ngi)002:330: mgon snying po dmigs dag phyag rgya spros bskal pa
NK034(ngi)002:331: 'khor ba'i mun sel la 'bum phrag lnga yi rang
NK034(ngi)002:332: gdung gis 'di nyid spros te dam du'o sems rig
NK034(ngi)002:333: kun gyi spyi phud mgon nga med sngon du phyag
NK034(ngi)002:334: rgya spros bskal pa snga mo stong ldan la bye
NK034(ngi)002:335: ba dgu yi gdung 'phel bas nges shes kun gyi
NK034(ngi)002:336: thog mar bzung bslab gnas kun gyii dang thog mgon
NK034(ngi)002:337: phyag rgya mig ldan stong du spros bskal pa sgyu
NK034(ngi)002:338: ma snang mdzad la yal yol gsum gyi yang gdung
NK034(ngi)002:339: gis 'di tshig gong ma'i gong mas bzung rim pa
NK034(ngi)002:340: sngon gyi skyed byed mgon babs byung med snang phyag
NK034(ngi)002:341: rgya spros bskal pa snying rjes kun 'dul la sang
NK034(ngi)002:342: seng lnga yi gdung 'phel bas snying po gsang ba
NK034(ngi)002:343: chen por bzung 'jigs pa kun bral seng ge mgon
NK034(ngi)002:344: sangs rgyas sras ni gcig pa spros bskal pa bzang
NK034(ngi)002:345: po rab gang la stong phrag bdun gyi gdung 'phel
NK034(ngi)002:346: bas 'byung ba'i sgra dang bral bar bzung rdzogs pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:347: yang thog tha ma mgon don dgongs nyag gcig rnal
NK034(ngi)002:348: du bzung bskal pa rtsod ldan chen po la brgya
NK034(ngi)002:349: phrag dgu yi gdung 'phel bas 'di tshig rtsod dang
NK034(ngi)002:350: bral bar bzung dran pa zad pa'i ye shes mgon
NK034(ngi)002:351: snying po rang tshig gcig par go bskal pa rtsod
NK034(ngi)002:352: dang ldan pa la bcu phrag dgu yi gdung 'dzin
NK034(ngi)002:353: pas nges pa'i phyag rgya dam par bzung de ltar
NK034(ngi)002:354: brjod kyis mi langs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi byin
NK034(ngi)002:355: rlabs las rang byung chen po'i yi ger ni gnas
NK034(ngi)002:356: pa'i ka dag chen po yi babs las 'di kun
NK034(ngi)002:357: rang byung shar byin brlabs rim pa 'di kun yang
NK034(ngi)002:358: thog ma babs las rang bstan no e ma rang
NK034(ngi)002:359: byung chen po'i tshig las kyang 'di ltar khyad par
NK034(ngi)002:360: rang byung tshig babs las byung zhing shar ba las
NK034(ngi)002:361: rang gsal chos rnams rang byung tshig phyis ni 'di
NK034(ngi)002:362: ltar yang dag go rgyud dang de yi rang 'grel
NK034(ngi)002:363: lo lha sngags la sogs phyag rgya bcu de las
NK034(ngi)002:364: 'di tshig phrag yas su snang ba yin no don
NK034(ngi)002:365: la sems snang mdzad don kun rang rdzogs te tshig
NK034(ngi)002:366: kun bdag por rang byung bas dgongs pa nyid ni
NK034(ngi)002:367: dang po las tshig rtsom mkhas pa 'di las ni
NK034(ngi)002:368: grangs las 'das rnams 'byung ba yin bdag 'dzin bdag
NK034(ngi)002:369: med sngon thog las mthar 'dzin 'dod pa dgag pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:370: phyir mngon sum rjes su dpags pa yi gtan tshigs
NK034(ngi)002:371: cha 'dzin tshig kun 'byung yid dpyod blo zhen dgag
NK034(ngi)002:372: pa'i phyir kun rdzob don dam grangs phye sogs tshig
NK034(ngi)002:373: ni 'di kun byin brlabs las 'di ltar rtsom pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:374: dpa' bo mkhas sems ni mthar zhen blo dgag phyir
NK034(ngi)002:375: phung po grangs dang khams sogs dang bstod dang yod
NK034(ngi)002:376: med chos dang ni chos min ji ltar rtsi ba
NK034(ngi)002:377: yi tshig kun 'di las rab brtson thob 'jig rten
NK034(ngi)002:378: mthun 'jug drang ba'i phyir sgra dang rig pa du
NK034(ngi)002:379: ma yang 'di yis rang byung tshig las shar phyir
NK034(ngi)002:380: 'gyur theg pa'i rang grangs kyis dbang po'i 'jug sgo
NK034(ngi)002:381: gsal ba'i phyir rim pa'i 'jug srol bcu gcig ni
NK034(ngi)002:382: 'di yi yon tan babs las snang rang 'od ji
NK034(ngi)002:383: ltar yod pa'i tshig 'di las spros so nye bar
NK034(ngi)002:384: bsdus grags dang ma grags tshig bcud ni 'di las
NK034(ngi)002:385: yang gsang chen por yang gyur te snang bar 'gyur
NK034(ngi)002:386: ba yin lha mis ji ltar 'dod pa'i tshig sgo
NK034(ngi)002:387: drug thob 'dod rang bkod tshig sngags lung sems dpa'i
NK034(ngi)002:388: lung rab snang 'di la gsang chen gnad du grags
NK034(ngi)002:389: de bzhin skye 'jig bstan bcos dang yod dang med
NK034(ngi)002:390: smra sde grangs spros mtha' gnyis rab 'byed yod snang
NK034(ngi)002:391: phyir dran sems nyid kyi sde grangs ni 'di kun
NK034(ngi)002:392: las byung sems kyi lung mjug sgo chen po'i shing
NK034(ngi)002:393: rta yang snang ba'i mdzad 'phros kha lo ni 'di
NK034(ngi)002:394: tshig dam pa'i 'khor lo'o grags pa'i sngags dang de
NK034(ngi)002:395: spel tshig rim pa mdo sde rang grags tshig bkod
NK034(ngi)002:396: pa rnams kyi thog mar ni 'di las 'aphro'o phan
NK034(ngi)002:397: sems ldan lung rgyal theg pa kun dngos so gzhi
NK034(ngi)002:398: rtsa rtsal gyi nan tan tshig 'di kun rgyan gyi
NK034(ngi)002:399: rgyal po las kha lo sgyur ba'i dpa' bo yin
NK034(ngi)002:400: byed pa'i las rgyal dkyil 'khor 'jug dpe med bris
NK034(ngi)002:401: pa'i sgra yig zer grangs mtha' 'gegs byed seng phrug
NK034(ngi)002:402: go bcos ma'i yang cha de 'phel bzung dpa' bar
NK034(ngi)002:403: 'gro ba'i las rgyas so mtho dman snyoms pa'i dge
NK034(ngi)002:404: 'bras lung dpe bral rnams kyi dang po'o de ltar
NK034(ngi)002:405: spros tshig du ma yis 'khor lo 'dzin pa'i sprul
NK034(ngi)002:406: pa'o mkha' gsal mkha' dag klong chen gyi spros pa
NK034(ngi)002:407: rnams kyi yang spros las skye sgo rab tu spangs
NK034(ngi)002:408: pa yis bla med 'dren pa'i dang por byung bde
NK034(ngi)002:409: bas bde ba 'byed pa yi rigs mthun kun gyi
NK034(ngi)002:410: gsang chen yin rigs la gnas shing rigs 'byed pa'o
NK034(ngi)002:411: gtso bo gtso bos blang ba'o ka dang rtogs dang
NK034(ngi)002:412: rab tu dgongs rim par rgyas dang de rjes ni
NK034(ngi)002:413: 'di las rab tu 'phel ba yin rab tu rtogs
NK034(ngi)002:414: phyir dkyil 'khor ni dam pa rnams ni 'di las
NK034(ngi)002:415: sprul thams cad las kyi mtha' rgyas kyang 'di las
NK034(ngi)002:416: rab tu yang 'phel lo 'di tshig byin rlabs brgyud
NK034(ngi)002:417: pa yang rab tu 'phel phyir 'byung ba'o e ma
NK034(ngi)002:418: hoh 'di ltar yang gsang don nyid la 'jug par
NK034(ngi)002:419: 'dod pa'i skal pa rab sngon du lus ngag yid
NK034(ngi)002:420: rnams kyi mngon par zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir sngon
NK034(ngi)002:421: du spyod pa brtsam par bya lus ni rgyug dang
NK034(ngi)002:422: nyal ba dang langs dang yan lag bskyod pa dang
NK034(ngi)002:423: skor ba dang ni phyag bya dang yan lag skor
NK034(ngi)002:424: dang mgo sgril dang ji ltar dran pa'i las rnams
NK034(ngi)002:425: dang gar dang phyag rgya bsgyur ba dang ji ltar
NK034(ngi)002:426: dmigs pa'i las rnams bya 'di ltar su yis byas
NK034(ngi)002:427: pa'i mi lus kyi mngon zhen rang bcad nas lus
NK034(ngi)002:428: kun ru shan phyed par ni 'di yis 'gyur ro
NK034(ngi)002:429: sprul pa'i sku de 'das ngag gi spyod pa brtsam
NK034(ngi)002:430: sngags dang kha ton chos kyi sgra yod dang med
NK034(ngi)002:431: dang snang ba dang yid spyod tshig ni sna tshogs
NK034(ngi)002:432: brjod byol song sna tshogs brda skad dang skad ni
NK034(ngi)002:433: rnam pa sna tshogs pa 'di ltar su yis byas
NK034(ngi)002:434: pa'i mi ngag gi mngon zhen rang chod nas 'khor
NK034(ngi)002:435: 'das ru shan 'dis phyed do de 'das nyid kyi
NK034(ngi)002:436: 'og tu yang sems kyi spyod pa brtsam par bya
NK034(ngi)002:437: dga' dang mi dga' bde sdug dang rtag dang mi
NK034(ngi)002:438: rtag la sogs pa lta sgom spyod pa'i bsam pa
NK034(ngi)002:439: dang chos dang chos min la sogs dang 'dod chags
NK034(ngi)002:440: zhe sdang gti mug dang dge dang mi dge la
NK034(ngi)002:441: sogs pa'i bsam dpyod rnam pa sna tshogs bya 'di
NK034(ngi)002:442: ltar su yis byas pa'i mi sems kyi mngon zhen
NK034(ngi)002:443: rang chod nas 'khor 'das ru shan phyed pa'o de
NK034(ngi)002:444: ltar sngon du 'gro byas nas mngon sum don la
NK034(ngi)002:445: blta bya'i phyir lus dang ngag yid rab tu gcun
NK034(ngi)002:446: lus ni seng ge lta bu dang drang srong dang
NK034(ngi)002:447: ni glang chen tshul 'di las g.yo bar ma byas
NK034(ngi)002:448: na sangs rgyas sum stong nyid dang yang bskal pa
NK034(ngi)002:449: dag ni mnyam pa yin ngag ni ji ltar lkugs
NK034(ngi)002:450: pa bzhin su dang brda tsam nyid mi bya 'di
NK034(ngi)002:451: ltar su yis byas pa'i mi sems kyi 'phro 'du
NK034(ngi)002:452: rang chod do 'di ltar lus ngag sus gcun pa
NK034(ngi)002:453: chos kyi dbyings kyi snang ba la 'di yis goms
NK034(ngi)002:454: par 'gyur ba yin de ltar lus la sogs pa
NK034(ngi)002:455: yi gnad kun rab tu gzir ba yis rig pa
NK034(ngi)002:456: nyid dang mngon sum du bla ma'i lung las shes
NK034(ngi)002:457: pa yin dbyings dang rig pa'i lta stangs ni sgrib
NK034(ngi)002:458: byed bral ba'i nam mkha' lta dbyings kyi nang du
NK034(ngi)002:459: lu gu rgyud rnam par bzhag cing 'bral mi bya
NK034(ngi)002:460: 'di ltar su yis mthong ba'i mi thog ma'i kun
NK034(ngi)002:461: tu bzang po dang skal pa nyid ni mnyam pa'o
NK034(ngi)002:462: de nas thig le mthong ba yin de gtad snang
NK034(ngi)002:463: ba gong 'phel bas rang ngo mthong bas 'di ltar
NK034(ngi)002:464: ro yar mtshams las ni sor bzhi las bral ba'i
NK034(ngi)002:465: skyes bu skal bzang ba 'khor bar 'jug pa ga
NK034(ngi)002:466: la srid gru chad rnam pa gang snang ba sprul
NK034(ngi)002:467: pa'i yon tan 'di yis 'grub mthong ba'i yul tsam
NK034(ngi)002:468: gang snang ba tshom bu la ni de bzhin no
NK034(ngi)002:469: phyir snang 'gag pa gang yin pa skad cig ma
NK034(ngi)002:470: ni bcu drug la 'di yang de ltar 'gyur ba'o
NK034(ngi)002:471: ma smin la sogs thig le dang de bzhin sku
NK034(ngi)002:472: la thug gi bar drug dang bcu dang lnga gsum
NK034(ngi)002:473: la gdon mi za ste longs skur ro nang lus
NK034(ngi)002:474: zad pa'i sar phyin tshe sor mo la sogs de
NK034(ngi)002:475: bzhin snang 'di gtad 'byung ba rang dengs so skye
NK034(ngi)002:476: dang 'jug pa'i khyad par gyis chos kun zad pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:477: rang sa la ci yang 'dzin pa med pa ni
NK034(ngi)002:478: gnas pa yin no sprul pa'i sku 'di ni 'jug
NK034(ngi)002:479: pa'i shugs kyis dbang skye ba'i rang dbang sus thob
NK034(ngi)002:480: pa de yang de la gtad nas ni yang dus
NK034(ngi)002:481: 'di ltar byas pa na snang ba'i rang sgra sil
NK034(ngi)002:482: skad de sngon du log ste 'khrul par snang 'dis
NK034(ngi)002:483: ni sems can don kun byed rig pa mnyam par
NK034(ngi)002:484: gcig pa'i phyir stong phrag gsum rnams sems can gyi
NK034(ngi)002:485: 'pho ba chen po 'dis 'grub po de bzhin rim
NK034(ngi)002:486: dang cig car gyi lus ni 'di yis 'grub pa
NK034(ngi)002:487: yin de kun lus zad mtshan las grol 'di kun
NK034(ngi)002:488: 'bras bu nges pa yis sa mchog dkyil 'khor chen
NK034(ngi)002:489: po 'grub 'di ltar thabs las yang dag byung sangs
NK034(ngi)002:490: rgyas 'grub par 'dod pa'i mis 'di thabs ldan na
NK034(ngi)002:491: de bzhin no gzhan spyod snyam byed nyid yin pas
NK034(ngi)002:492: dngos po mthong ba ma yin no de phyir 'di
NK034(ngi)002:493: kun dkon pa'i tshig rtag tu rin chen gter 'di
NK034(ngi)002:494: ltos 'di ltar zad pa la spyod na 'dis ni
NK034(ngi)002:495: sangs rgyas stong phrag gsum 'di yis legs par zhal
NK034(ngi)002:496: mthong yin 'di tshig gsang ba nyid las byung skyes
NK034(ngi)002:497: bu rnams kyis 'di ltar bya gsang chen yang gsang
NK034(ngi)002:498: dam pa'o e ma 'di ltar 'byung 'dod skyes bu
NK034(ngi)002:499: gang thabs kyi yan lag 'di lta bu rnam pa
NK034(ngi)002:500: sna tshogs nyid la ni 'di ltar de yi sngon
NK034(ngi)002:501: du sbyang sems kyi rim pa ci sbyangs pa 'dis
NK034(ngi)002:502: ni mi rtag sems la 'byor ji ltar sgra yi
NK034(ngi)002:503: rnal 'byor pas sa chu me rlung 'byung ba bzhi
NK034(ngi)002:504: sgra don rnams la goms pa yis rigs drug rnams
NK034(ngi)002:505: kyi rang skad kyis mngon shes 'char ba 'dis 'grub
NK034(ngi)002:506: bo zhag rim dus ni rnam drug gis 'di yi
NK034(ngi)002:507: skad kun rang dus shes 'grus pa med par sus
NK034(ngi)002:508: shes pa ma 'ongs da lta 'das pa yi sems
NK034(ngi)002:509: rgyud ji ltar shes par 'gyur gzhan gyi don byed
NK034(ngi)002:510: sprul pa pos 'di la sngon du ma sbyangs na
NK034(ngi)002:511: sprul pa'i sa bon 'jog par ni nus pa nyid
NK034(ngi)002:512: ni mi thob bo des na 'byung ba'i sgra la
NK034(ngi)002:513: bslab bya byed zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir lag ni
NK034(ngi)002:514: bya byed sna tshogs bya de bzhin 'dus byas rnam
NK034(ngi)002:515: pa yis dbang po'i mngon zhen bzlog pa ste yul
NK034(ngi)002:516: rnams goms pa'i gnad kyis sbyang ji ltar gnyid dang
NK034(ngi)002:517: rmi lam gyi dus bzhi 'byung ba gnad kyis dbye
NK034(ngi)002:518: tshad ni gnad la phebs pas bzung thig le phyii
NK034(ngi)002:519: nang bslab bya'i phyir gang zag rnam pa gnyis don
NK034(ngi)002:520: bya bcos ma 'dus byas sgom pa yis dang po
NK034(ngi)002:521: po sems yengs zhen pa dgag 'bras bu cig car
NK034(ngi)002:522: ma yin pas snang ba rim gyis goms par bya
NK034(ngi)002:523: mig sman la sogs sgo lnga yi sman gyi rim
NK034(ngi)002:524: pa sbyar bar bya 'di kun gsang ba'i thabs yin
NK034(ngi)002:525: no lam gyi rtags ni lus las ni mngon par
NK034(ngi)002:526: phyi rol snang gyur pa'i sman nyid kyang ni de
NK034(ngi)002:527: bzhin no 'di kun 'jig rten drang don du skal
NK034(ngi)002:528: ba can gyi spyod yul lo 'di yi thabs ni
NK034(ngi)002:529: sna tshogs pas gzhan gyi 'dod zhen mtha' dgag phyir
NK034(ngi)002:530: rab tu gsang bar byung ba'o khams la bslab pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:531: thabs yod pas dran rdzogs phyag rgya'i ngang du sbyor
NK034(ngi)002:532: dbang po'i zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir kar+m+aa rak+sha g+hi
NK034(ngi)002:533: ham ti phung po'i zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir b+he
NK034(ngi)002:534: ga ra na so gad gling yul kun zhen pa
NK034(ngi)002:535: bzlog pa'i phyir pu k+aa ri la b+ha d+hu tri
NK034(ngi)002:536: sems kyi dngos po spur ba'i phyir ram pa ka
NK034(ngi)002:537: la sa mi khye byung tshor gnas su gcod pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:538: phyir ma tang pha pher rasmi ti 'dus tshogs snang
NK034(ngi)002:539: ba ngos gzung phyir kha ta re ka sa mig
NK034(ngi)002:540: rlung rig pa btson rar gzhug pa'i phyir a ke
NK034(ngi)002:541: ra na b+he tsaka sha 'khrul pa'i rang rgyud khungs
NK034(ngi)002:542: bcad phyir ya ri mu da sa g+hu li rigs
NK034(ngi)002:543: drug rim gyis bsgral ba'i phyir ya sing ra rlung
NK034(ngi)002:544: ba la y+aa 'khor ba dong nas gdon pa'i phyir
NK034(ngi)002:545: ma ma ko ling s+aa m+aa ta chos can thur
NK034(ngi)002:546: du gzhug pa'i phyir g+ha ring yam pa ri mang
NK034(ngi)002:547: ti rol ba'i byung khungs spur ba'i phyir bu ga
NK034(ngi)002:548: sing ha pha g+ha la zhen pa'i phreng thag gcad
NK034(ngi)002:549: pa'i phyir ra mi pi p+ai khe ta pa lug
NK034(ngi)002:550: rgyud ar la gtad pa'i phyir bi khu ma la
NK034(ngi)002:551: pa tam ki lha yi phyag rgya blta ba'i phyir
NK034(ngi)002:552: sa m+aa nyi wa d+he ra pa lta sgom log
NK034(ngi)002:553: pa dag bya'i phyir badz+ra sat+wa di d+ho me sa
NK034(ngi)002:554: lam dus gcig gcad pa'i phyir g+he ba su g+har
NK034(ngi)002:555: rna ma yee yid dpyod lta ba khungs gcad phyir
NK034(ngi)002:556: d+har+m+aa pa ti sa g+hu l+ai sku gsum lam du
NK034(ngi)002:557: bslang ba'i phyir rasmi sa m+aa kha rgad tshe snang
NK034(ngi)002:558: ba dngos su blang ba'i phyir ru pa sa mi
NK034(ngi)002:559: mi ta lam sgra yi zhen pa mtha' gcad phyir
NK034(ngi)002:560: nga tig pa yang ka li s+aa bsam gtan chen
NK034(ngi)002:561: po'i sa non phyir ga tsha pa la sa i
NK034(ngi)002:562: tam phrin las mthar ru dbyung ba'i phyir karma e
NK034(ngi)002:563: ka a nu s+aa sangs rgyas mngon zhen bzlog pa'i
NK034(ngi)002:564: phyir sangs tri ma ma kar+m+aa ta rgyal sras rnams
NK034(ngi)002:565: kyi gnas btsal phyir nga la khe pa ki li
NK034(ngi)002:566: sa 'di kun rang shugs tshig tu byung e ma
NK034(ngi)002:567: ho bcom pa dang ni ldan pa dang 'das pa
NK034(ngi)002:568: yang dag lam yin no 'di tshig lam min gdams
NK034(ngi)002:569: pa yin bstan zhing bshad med brjod ma yin gsungs
NK034(ngi)002:570: pa ma yin byin brlabs yin bris shing bkod med
NK034(ngi)002:571: rang byung yin gnas dang dus med sngon thog yin
NK034(ngi)002:572: chos med snying po thugs gsang yin sus kyang nyan
NK034(ngi)002:573: med rang shar yin thos pa med cing rang bsgrags
NK034(ngi)002:574: yin byas pa 'di kun ma yin tshig 'di yod
NK034(ngi)002:575: 'gro ba sangs rgyas yin pha rol mthong ba'i gsang
NK034(ngi)002:576: chen lam sems yod ma yin sprul pa yin 'khor
NK034(ngi)002:577: ba'i spyi mdud grol ba'o shes bya ma yin lam
NK034(ngi)002:578: sna thag stong pa ma yin mngon sum yul yod
NK034(ngi)002:579: med ma yin thabs gsang ba lha med 'di la
NK034(ngi)002:580: sngags yod min pha rol phyin pa drug gi gzhi
NK034(ngi)002:581: bsnyen gnas la sogs 'di tshul lo de bzhin du
NK034(ngi)002:582: yang bye brag smra don dam kun rdzob gzugs kyis
NK034(ngi)002:583: so rgyud kyi rtsa ba 'di nyid rang lha yi
NK034(ngi)002:584: rnal 'byor 'di sngags yin lung chen rnams kyi dam
NK034(ngi)002:585: pa 'di chos rnams ro gcig 'dres pa'i rten sku
NK034(ngi)002:586: gsung thugs kyi dbye ba'o bla med 'khor lo bskor
NK034(ngi)002:587: ba'i gnas dbang po rnams kyi dmigs gtad yin shes
NK034(ngi)002:588: rab rnams kyi rtog pa'i gnas sku gsum lam du
NK034(ngi)002:589: slong ba'i rten thig le mngon du 'byin pa'i mig
NK034(ngi)002:590: thar pa'i skas kun slong bar byed lam du 'jug
NK034(ngi)002:591: pa'i sa mkhan yin skal ldan 'dzin pa'i lcags kyur
NK034(ngi)002:592: snang chos sku rang 'jog gnas lugs yin sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)002:593: kun gyi phyag byed gnas yul rnams gcod pa'i ral
NK034(ngi)002:594: grir snang grol ba rnams ni 'di nyid la rnam
NK034(ngi)002:595: par brten nas grol ba'o sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NK034(ngi)002:596: sras gcig po bstan pa rnams kyi btsas su rang
NK034(ngi)002:597: byung ba rang byung gi yi ge chen por bskal
NK034(ngi)002:598: pa kun gyi thog mar rang byung ba byin brlabs
NK034(ngi)002:599: las rang bkod pa sprul pa sku yi sa bon
NK034(ngi)002:600: 'phel bar byed pa rab tu dkon pa'i tshig rdzogs
NK034(ngi)002:601: so s+aa m+aa y+aa rgya rgya rgya sho lo ka
